    public static enum Logger.LEVEL
extends java.lang.Enum<Logger.LEVEL>
    The basic levels of a given log message.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      CONFIG

      • CONFIG

        public static final Logger.LEVEL CONFIG
        A message with user configuration data. The priority of this kind of message is between INFO and TRACE_LEVEL3. Internally JPARSEC does not use information or configuration messages, but only trace messages (and warnings/errors).

      • INFO

        public static final Logger.LEVEL INFO
        An informative message, with a priority just below the warning level. Internally JPARSEC does not use information or configuration messages, but only trace messages (and warnings/errors).

      • WARNING

        public static final Logger.LEVEL WARNING
        A warning to the user.

      • ERROR

        public static final Logger.LEVEL ERROR
        A message indicating an error.
